[[File:Black Sea Coast of Batumi, Georgia (Europe).jpg|thumb|right|220px|Black Sea in [[Batumi]], [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]]]]
[[File:The Swallow's Nest castle on the Aurora cliffs of cape Ai-Todor (2005-09-229).jpg|thumb|220px|[[Swallow's Nest (Crimea)|Swallow's Nest in Ukraine]]]]
