* [[Gospel of John|Gospel According to John]], &lt;small&gt;Jn&lt;/small&gt;
* [[Acts of the Apostles]], &lt;small&gt;Ac&lt;/small&gt; (continues Luke)

'''[[Pauline Epistles]]'''

* [[Epistle to the Romans]], &lt;small&gt;Ro&lt;/small&gt;
* [[First Epistle to the Corinthians]], &lt;small&gt;1Co&lt;/small&gt;

