*c. 500 BC: The earliest reference to [[Pachisi]] in the ''[[Mahabharata]]'', the [[Indian subcontinent|Indian]] epic.
*c. 400 BC: Two ornately decorated ''[[Liubo]]'' game boards from a royal tomb of the [[Zhongshan (state)|State of Zhongshan]] in [[China]].&lt;ref&gt;{{cite book | last = Rawson | first = Jessica | authorlink = Jessica Rawson | title = Mysteries of Ancient China | publisher = British Museum Press | year = 1996 | location = London | pages = 159–161 | isbn = 0-7141-1472-3}}&lt;/ref&gt;
